title: Transgender community stages protest in eastern India over rising rape incidents
text:
Transgender community stages protest in eastern India over rising rape incidents 11:57am BST - 01:15 
Members of the transgender community stage a protest condemning the rising number of rape and harrassment cases in the country. No reporter narration. ▲ Hide Transcript ▶ View Transcript
